  <section class="category">
    <h2>Traditional Unions</h2>
    <p class="category-summary">The project aims to analyze and document workers’ workplace resistance and unionization practices in location-based digital labour platforms in India, develop context-appropriate resistance strategies for technology-mediated labour and re-design algorithmic technologies to support precarious workers.</p>
    
